<L>__{exterior atomic hoagie shop night}
<A>__{rocky passes an all night sandwich shop... in the window hangs the sign "atomic hoagie shop, inc." out front are several young men and women. they are much too young to be out so late... a boy with a badly chipped tooth beckons to rocky.}
